data.title: Franklin County Voter Guide
data.meta_description: Your next election is on Tuesday, September 3, 2024. Everything you need to know about voting in Franklin County: registering to vote, voting by mail, voting early, or on Election Day.
data.text:
County Profile

Franklin County

The next election in Franklin County is Massachusetts Primary Election on Tuesday, September 3, 2024.

More than 263 positions are up for election ranging from federal positions including U.S. Senate - Massachusetts to county offices like Hampshire County Register of Probate.
